data.description: Stunning 2-Bed, 2-Bath Condo in South Shore - Your Dream Home Awaits! Welcome to your new oasis in South Shore. This immaculate 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom condo is a true gem that offers a spacious living experience. This condo features an extra-large primary bedroom with large walk-in closet, creating a serene and private retreat for you to unwind and relax after a long day.; an updated kitchen with brand new appliances; and say goodbye to trips to the laundromat! Enjoy the convenience of an in-unit washer and dryer.  You'll love the fact that this condo is within walking distance of Lake Michigan and the South Shore Cultural Center. This condo boasts beautiful hardwood floors, and the bedrooms have brand new carpet. The entire unit has been freshly painted, giving it a modern and inviting feel.
